WEBVTT

00:04:01.040 --> 00:04:03.960
But in the other group,
which did not have ReThink,

00:04:04.020 --> 00:04:07.970
only 32 percent of those teenagers
decided not to post the messages.

00:04:08.040 --> 00:04:11.210
So ReThink stopped a hurt
before it could happen.

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:17.640
In 2012, Microsoft did a survey with kids
between eight and 17 years of age.

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:21.960
This survey, across 25 countries 
said that India stands at number three

00:04:22.010 --> 00:04:24.270
when it comes to online bullying.

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:29.940
53 percent of kids in the survey reported
that they were victims of online bullying.